    "toc3": "Jol",
    "mt2": "This book is the account of Joel foretelling about many nations conquering the Israeli people and about God restoring them. We call this book",
    "mt1": "Joel"
  ],
  "contents": [
    "c": "1",
    "style": "p",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "I am",
    "text": "I am",
    "text": " Joel, the son of Pethuel. ",
    "add": "This is",
    "text": "This is",
    "text": " a message that Yahweh gave to me.",
    "style": "s1",
    "text": "The attack by locusts",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "2",
    "text": "You leaders ",
    "add": "of Israel",
    "text": "of Israel",
    "text": ", and everyone else who lives in this country, listen ",
    "add": "to this message",
    "text": "to this message",
    "text": "!",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "Nothing [RHQ] like this has ever happened during the time that we have lived",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "or the time when our ancestors lived.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "3",
    "text": "Tell your children about it,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and tell your children to tell it to their children,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and tell your grandchildren to tell it to their children.",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "4",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "I am talking about",
    "text": "I am talking about",
    "text": " the locusts that have eaten our crops.",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "The first swarm of locusts came and cut ",
    "add": "many of the leaves of the crops",
    "text": "many of the leaves of the crops",
    "text": ";",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "then another swarm came and ate ",
    "add": "the rest of the leaves",
    "text": "the rest of the leaves",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "then another swarm came hopping along,",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "and finally another swarm came",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and they destroyed ",
    "add": "everything else",
    "text": "everything else",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "5",
    "text": "You people who are drunk, wake up!",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "Wake up and wail loudly,",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "because all the grapes are ruined,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and so there will be no new wine [MTY]!",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "6",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "Huge swarms of",
    "text": "Huge swarms of",
    "text": " locusts have entered our country.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "They are like",
    "text": "They are like",
    "text": " [MET] a powerful army",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "that has very many soldiers",
    "text": "that has very many soldiers",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "with the result that",
    "text": "with the result that",
    "text": " no one can count them.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "The locusts have teeth that are ",
    "add": "as sharp as",
    "text": "as sharp as",
    "text": " the teeth of lions [DOU]!",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "7",
    "text": "They have destroyed our grapevines and our fig trees",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "by",
    "text": "by",
    "text": " stripping off ",
    "add": "and eating all",
    "text": "and eating all",
    "text": " the bark,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "with the result that the branches are white ",
    "add": "and \u25C4bare/have no leaves on them\u25BA",
    "text": "and \u25C4bare/have no leaves on them\u25BA",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "8",
    "text": "Cry like [SIM] a young woman cries",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "when the young man to whom she was \u25C4engaged/promised to marry\u25BA has died.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "9",
    "text": "There is no grain or wine for us to offer ",
    "add": "as sacrifices",
    "text": "as sacrifices",
    "text": " at the temple,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "so",
    "text": "so",
    "text": " the priests who serve Yahweh are mourning/weeping.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "10",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "The crops in",
    "text": "The crops in",
    "text": " the fields have been ruined;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "it is as though",
    "text": "it is as though",
    "text": " [PRS] the ground is mourning.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "The grain has been destroyed,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "there are no ",
    "add": "grapes to make",
    "text": "grapes to make",
    "text": " wine,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and there is no ",
    "add": "more olive ",
    "text": "more olive ",
    "text": " oil.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "11",
    "text": "You farmers, grieve!",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "You who take care of grapevines, wail,",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "because the grain has been destroyed;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "there is no wheat or barley growing.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "12",
    "text": "The grapevines and the fig trees have withered,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and the pomegranate ",
    "add": "trees",
    "text": "trees",
    "text": " and palm ",
    "add": "trees",
    "text": "trees",
    "text": " and apricot ",
    "add": "trees",
    "text": "trees",
    "text": " have also dried up.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "The people are no longer joyful.",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "13",
    "text": "You priests, put on ",
    "add": "rough",
    "text": "rough",
    "text": " sack clothes and wail.",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "You who serve God ",
    "add": "by offering sacrifices",
    "text": "by offering sacrifices",
    "text": " on the altar,",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "wear those rough sack clothes all night ",
    "add": "to show that you are mourning",
    "text": "to show that you are mourning",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "because there is no grain or wine to be offered at the temple of your God.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "14",
    "text": "Tell the people that they should \u25C4fast/abstain from eating food\u25BA.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Tell the leaders and the other people to gather at the temple",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and to cry ",
    "add": "out",
    "text": "out",
    "text": " to Yahweh ",
    "add": "there",
    "text": "there",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "15",
    "text": "Terrible things are happening to us!",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "It will soon be the time when Yahweh, ",
    "add": "who is",
    "text": "who is",
    "text": " the Almighty God, ",
    "add": "will really punish us",
    "text": "will really punish us",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "when he",
    "text": "when he",
    "text": " will cause us to experience more disasters.",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "16",
    "text": "Our crops are already gone,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and no ",
    "add": "one is",
    "text": "one is",
    "text": " rejoicing at all [DOU] at the temple of our God.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "17",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "When we plant",
    "text": "When we plant",
    "text": " seeds, ",
    "add": "they do not grow",
    "text": "they do not grow",
    "text": ";",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "they dry up in the ground,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "so there are no crops to harvest.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Our barns/storehouses are empty;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "there is no grain ",
    "add": "to store in them",
    "text": "to store in them",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "18",
    "text": "Our cattle groan, searching for a pasture with some grass to eat,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and the sheep bleat because they are suffering.",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "19",
    "text": "Yahweh, I cry ",
    "add": "out",
    "text": "out",
    "text": " to you,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "because our pastures and our forests have dried up in the hot sunshine [MET].",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "20",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "It is as though",
    "text": "It is as though",
    "text": " even the wild animals cry ",
    "add": "out",
    "text": "out",
    "text": " to you",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "because all the streams have dried up.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "The rivers and streams are all dry,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and the grass in the pastures is all parched.",
    "c": "2",
    "style": "s1",
    "text": "A warning about the locusts",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "1",
    "text": "Blow trumpets on Zion ",
    "add": "Hill",
    "text": "Hill",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "God\u2019s sacred hill ",
    "add": "in Jerusalem",
    "text": "in Jerusalem",
    "text": "!",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Tell the people of Judah that they should tremble,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "because it will soon be the time for Yahweh ",
    "add": "to punish us further",
    "text": "to punish us further",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "That will be a very",
    "text": "That will be a very",
    "text": " dark and gloomy day;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "there will be ",
    "add": "black",
    "text": "black",
    "text": " clouds and it will be very dark.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "A huge ",
    "add": "swarm of locusts",
    "text": "swarm of locusts",
    "text": " has covered the mountains like [SIM] a black ",
    "add": "cloud",
    "text": "cloud",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Nothing like this has ever happened before,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and nothing like this will ever ",
    "add": "happen",
    "text": "happen",
    "text": " again.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "3",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "It is as though the locusts bring",
    "text": "It is as though the locusts bring",
    "text": " flames of fire",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "from which no one can escape.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "In front of them, the land was ",
    "add": "beautiful",
    "text": "beautiful",
    "text": " like [SIM] the garden of Eden,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "but behind them ",
    "add": "the land is like",
    "text": "the land is like",
    "text": " a desert",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and nothing survives.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "4",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "The locusts",
    "text": "The locusts",
    "text": " resemble horses,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and they run like [SIM] war horses.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "5",
    "text": "Leaping over the mountaintops,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "they make a noise like rumbling chariots,",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "like [SIM] a mighty army that is preparing for a battle,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "or like [SIM] the roar of a fire that burns up stubble ",
    "add": "in a field",
    "text": "in a field",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "6",
    "text": "When people see them coming,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "they become very pale and frightened.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "7",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "The locusts",
    "text": "The locusts",
    "text": " climb over walls like soldiers do;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "they march along in columns",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "and never turn aside ",
    "add": "from their columns",
    "text": "from their columns",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "8",
    "text": "They rush straight ahead",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "without pushing each other.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "Even though people throw",
    "text": "Even though people throw",
    "text": " spears and javelins at them,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "that will not cause them to stop.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "9",
    "text": "They swarm over the city walls and enter our houses;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "they enter through our windows like [SIM] thieves do.",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "10",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "It is as though",
    "text": "It is as though",
    "text": " they cause the earth to shake and the sky to tremble.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "The sun and the moon become dark",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "and the stars do not shine",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "because there are so many locusts in the sky",
    "text": "because there are so many locusts in the sky",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "11",
    "text": "Yahweh leads this army ",
    "add": "of countless locusts",
    "text": "of countless locusts",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and they obey his commands.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "This time when he is judging and punishing us is very terrible,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "with the result that it seems that",
    "text": "with the result that it seems that",
    "text": " no one [RHQ] can survive it.",
    "style": "s1",
    "text": "Yahweh calls them to repent",
    "style": "p",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "12",
    "text": "But Yahweh says,",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\u201CIn spite of ",
    "add": "these disasters that you have experienced",
    "text": "these disasters that you have experienced",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "you can return to me with all your inner beings.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Weep, and mourn, and \u25C4fast/abstain from eating food\u25BA ",
    "add": "to show that you are sorry for having abandoned me",
    "text": "to show that you are sorry for having abandoned me",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "13",
    "text": "Do not tear your clothes",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "to show that you are sorry",
    "text": "to show that you are sorry",
    "text": ";",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "instead, show [MET] that you are sorry.\u201D",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Yahweh is merciful and kind;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "he does not quickly become angry;",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "he faithfully loves ",
    "add": "people",
    "text": "people",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "He does not quickly become angry;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "instead, he greatly and faithfully loves ",
    "add": "you",
    "text": "you",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and he does not like to punish you.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "14",
    "text": "No one knows [RHQ] if he will change his mind ",
    "add": "about punishing you",
    "text": "about punishing you",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and if instead he will act mercifully ",
    "add": "toward you",
    "text": "toward you",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "If he does that, he will bless you",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "by giving you plenty of grain and wine",
    "text": "by giving you plenty of grain and wine",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "in order that you can offer ",
    "add": "some of ",
    "text": "some of ",
    "text": " those things as sacrifices to him.",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "15",
    "text": "Blow the trumpets on Zion ",
    "add": "Hill",
    "text": "Hill",
    "text": "!",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "Gather the people together!",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Show by fasting that you are sorry ",
    "add": "for the sins that you have committed",
    "text": "for the sins that you have committed",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "16",
    "text": "Perform the rituals to cause yourselves to be acceptable to Yahweh.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Gather everyone together\u2014",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "the old people and the children, even the babies,",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "and summon brides and bridegrooms from their rooms.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "17",
    "text": "Tell the priests who serve Yahweh to cry between the altar and the entrance to the temple",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and to pray ",
    "add": "this",
    "text": "this",
    "text": ":",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\u201CYahweh, rescue/save ",
    "add": "us",
    "text": "us",
    "text": " your people;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "do not allow people from other nations to despise us;",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "do not allow them to ridicule us and say,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\u2018Why has [RHQ] their God ",
    "add": "abandoned them",
    "text": "abandoned them",
    "text": "?\u2019\u201D",
    "style": "s1",
    "text": "Yahweh promised to prosper them again",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "18",
    "text": "But Yahweh ",
    "add": "showed that he",
    "text": "showed that he",
    "text": " was concerned about his people",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and that he would act mercifully toward them.",
    "style": "p",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "19",
    "text": "When the people prayed,",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Yahweh answered and said,",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\u201CI will give you ",
    "add": "plenty of",
    "text": "plenty of",
    "text": " grain and wine and ",
    "add": "olive",
    "text": "olive",
    "text": " oil,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and you will be satisfied.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "And I will no longer allow other nations to insult you.",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "20",
    "text": "Another army ",
    "add": "of locusts will come",
    "text": "of locusts will come",
    "text": " from the north ",
    "add": "to attack you",
    "text": "to attack you",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "but I will force them to continue ",
    "add": "past Jerusalem",
    "text": "past Jerusalem",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "into the desert.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Some will go into the Dead Sea in the east",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and some will go into the ",
    "add": "Mediterranean",
    "text": "Mediterranean",
    "text": " Sea in the west.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "There",
    "text": "There",
    "text": " they will ",
    "add": "all die, and their bodies",
    "text": "all die, and their bodies",
    "text": " will stink.\u201D",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Yahweh does great things!",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "21",
    "text": "He does wonderful things!",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "So even the ground should rejoice!",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "22",
    "text": "And the wild animals should not be afraid,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "because the meadows will soon become green again;",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "the fig trees and ",
    "add": "other",
    "text": "other",
    "text": " trees will be full of fruit,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and the grapevines will be covered with grapes.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "23",
    "text": "You people of Jerusalem,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "rejoice about what Yahweh, your God, ",
    "add": "will be doing for you",
    "text": "will be doing for you",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "He will send abundant rain at the \u25C4right time/time when it is needed\u25BA\u2014",
    "style": "q2",
